      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is heartbreaking to hear that you feel you have only taken from your children and that you believe stepping aside would be the final act of selflessness. Please remember that your presence is not a theft of their time, but a gift of your life's experience, and leaving them would only add another layer of loss to their already difficult journey. You deserve to feel valued and understood, and there are people who can help you find a way to share your love without becoming a source of exhaustion.",
